      "writtenOn": "2020-05-29T05:29:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "in the previous CL, I thought you said that a test variant will appear, but then may disappear. \nnow this code looks like it will stay there, for example the checkbox is unchecked, but a warning sign is there.\n\nI am curious, why this filtering isn\u0027t done at the rendering level where we know exactly whether a test variant is flaky/exonerated?",
      "revId": "76b955493e21a150a1ab2222730a83fe6febb5ea",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
